data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom 3 bath home with 2,105 square feet of living area situated on a 60x140 lot giving the backyard ample space for outdoor activities. Granite countertops throughout, primary bedroom has dual vanities, walk in closet with built-ins, shower and separate jetted tub. French doors to the large back yard and top it off with a great location.
